{"tid":2436334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地檢測中心遺失本月3、4日檢測者資料","createTime":"2021-03-07T05:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T07:43:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"178a0533c958aa9f50126269983ffe33003ed7b3","tid":2436334,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎持續，不少市民會到社區檢測中心接受檢測，《香港01》接獲投訴，指位於油麻地的檢測中心近日遺失檢測者資料，無法通知陰性者結果，恐亦未能把陽性者送入醫院隔離治療。投訴人稱，該中心的職員向他指出，在本月3、4日到中心接受檢測者，其資料都已遺失，承辦商無法得知檢測者的任何資料，故無法通知相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日（7日）以市民身份前往油麻地梁顯利社區檢測中心查詢，有承辦商職員透露，大批於3月3日曾接受免費檢測人士，不知道因何緣故，收不到檢測結果，前來中心查詢；致電熱線查詢時，職員則形容梁顯利社區中心「有啲問題」，<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料該中心的承辦商是「金域」。記者正就事件向食物及衞生局查詢。"},{"pid":"ac19e40b7a0a954be3cb99fa132cd5ffb96e7f39","tid":2436334,"uid":66365,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔見左可以唔通報，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c9042d6496c601ee5380416fe3176cff67fb94","tid":2436334,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ac19e40b7a0a954be3cb99fa132cd5ffb96e7f39","tid":2436334,"uid":66365,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔見左可以唔通報，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"選委會唔見咗全港邏民資料啦夠"},{"pid":"e8d619cec798d714fd3e2b4f570e3367981cf83d","tid":2436334,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac19e40b7a0a954be3cb99fa132cd5ffb96e7f39","tid":2436334,"uid":66365,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔見左可以唔通報，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass